snippet: A federal judge in California largely sided with Ticketmaster in Songkick’s antitrust case, which could still go to trial.
abstract: United States District Court Judge Dale S Fischer of Los Angeles denies antitrust injunction by Songkick against Ticketmaster; firm contends its contracts with concert halls allow it to decide how tickets are allotted.
lead_paragraph: A federal judge in California largely sided with Ticketmaster in Songkick’s antitrust case, which could still go to trial.

headline.main: Songkick’s Request for an Injunction Against Ticketmaster Is Denied
